    "chunk_index": 0,
    "chunk_text": "Technical Details. Because each JSON object will be separated by a new line, they can't contain literal new line characters in their content, but they can contain escaped new lines ( \\n ), which is part of the JSON standard. But normally you won't have to worry about it, it's done automatically, continue reading. 🤓",
